n all over."},{"content":"Transfer onto paper towel to drain and allow to cool slightly before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to <em>The Basic Cookbook <\/em>or <em>Everyday Cookbook <\/em>for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","You can replace mozzarella with bocconcini in this recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","1h 30m","25h 25m","36 portions"]}